    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedAt", c."Description", c."Domain", c."InstructorId", c."IsDeleted", c."Language", c."Level", c."Tags", c."ThumbnailUrl", c."Title", c."UpdatedAt", u."Id" AS "Id0", u."Bio", u."CreatedAt" AS "CreatedAt0", u."Email", u."FullName", u."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", u."PasswordHash", u."PhoneNumber", u."ProfilePictureUrl", u."RefreshToken", u."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt" AS "UpdatedAt0", u."Username"
    FROM "Courses" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON c."InstructorId" = u."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__id_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted")
    LIMIT 1
) AS s
LEFT JOIN "UploadedFiles" AS u0 ON s."Id" = u0."CourseId"
LEFT JOIN "Enrollments" AS e ON s."Id" = e."CourseId"
ORDER BY s."Id", s."Id0", u0."Id", e."UserId"

    WHERE c."Id" = @__id_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted")
    LIMIT 1
) AS s
LEFT JOIN "UploadedFiles" AS u0 ON s."Id" = u0."CourseId"
LEFT JOIN "Enrollments" AS e ON s."Id" = e."CourseId"
ORDER BY s."Id", s."Id0", u0."Id", e."UserId"

2025-06-30 15:27:54.098 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (35ms) [Parameters=[@__id_0='?' (DbType = Guid)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT s."Id", s."CreatedAt", s."Description", s."Domain", s."InstructorId", s."IsDeleted", s."Language", s."Level", s."Tags", s."ThumbnailUrl", s."Title", s."UpdatedAt", s."Id0", s."Bio", s."CreatedAt0", s."Email", s."FullName", s."IsDeleted0", s."PasswordHash", s."PhoneNumber", s."ProfilePictureUrl", s."RefreshToken", s."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", s."RoleId", s."UpdatedAt0", s."Username", u0."Id", u0."CourseId", u0."Description", u0."FileName", u0."FileType", u0."Path", u0."Topic", u0."UploadedAt", e."UserId", e."CourseId", e."EnrolledAt"
FROM (
    SELECT c."Id", c."CreatedAt", c."Description", c."Domain", c."InstructorId", c."IsDeleted", c."Language", c."Level", c."Tags", c."ThumbnailUrl", c."Title", c."UpdatedAt", u."Id" AS "Id0", u."Bio", u."CreatedAt" AS "CreatedAt0", u."Email", u."FullName", u."IsDeleted" AS "IsDeleted0", u."PasswordHash", u."PhoneNumber", u."ProfilePictureUrl", u."RefreshToken", u."RefreshTokenExpiryTime", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt" AS "UpdatedAt0", u."Username"
    FROM "Courses" AS c
    INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON c."InstructorId" = u."Id"
    WHERE c."Id" = @__id_0 AND NOT (c."IsDeleted")
    LIMIT 1
) AS s
LEFT JOIN "UploadedFiles" AS u0 ON s."Id" = u0."CourseId"
LEFT JOIN "Enrollments" AS e ON s."Id" = e."CourseId"
ORDER BY s."Id", s."Id0", u0."Id", e."UserId"
